trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of all [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) elements in a project.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de todos os elementos [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) em um projeto.

trans-unit.source: The <see langword="Name" /> attribute of the new <see langword="Target" /> element.
trans-unit.target: O atributo <see langword="Name" /> do novo elemento <see langword="Target" />.

trans-unit.source: Adds a new [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) element to the end of the project.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona um novo elemento [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) ao fim do projeto.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> object representing the created <c>Target</c> element.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> que representa o elemento <c>Target</c> criado.

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" /> that is the destination of the elements copied from <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Array" /> unidimensional que é o destino dos elementos copiados de <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Array" /> must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Array" /> deve ter indexação com base em zero.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: O índice baseado em zero na <c>array</c> na qual a cópia começa.

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" /> to a compatible one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" />, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: Copia todo o <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" /> em um <see cref="T:System.Array" /> unidimensional compatível, começando no índice especificado da matriz de destino.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating the number of <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> objects in the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica o número de objetos do <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> no <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: An integer value representing the number of <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> objects in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um valor inteiro que representa o número de <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> objetos na coleção.

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> object in the collection represents a element in the project.
trans-unit.target: Cada <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> objeto na coleção representa um elemento no projeto.

trans-unit.source: The <see langword="Name" /> attribute of the Target element to search for.
trans-unit.target: O atributo <see langword="Name" /> do elemento Target a ser pesquisado.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> exists in the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Determina se o <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> especificado existe no <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <c>Target</c> element exists; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se o elemento <c>Target</c> existe; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets an enumerator that iterates through the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um enumerador que itera por meio do <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> for the entire <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> para todo o <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: This method allows the caller to use the `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]) to iterate through the individual <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> objects in the <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Esse método permite que o chamador usar o `foreach` instrução de linguagem c# (`for each` na [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]) para percorrer o indivíduo <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> objetos no <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether access to the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" /> is synchronized (thread safe).
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se o acesso à <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" /> é sincronizado (thread-safe).

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if access to the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" /> is synchronized (thread safe); otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> caso o acesso ao <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" /> seja sincronizado (thread-safe); do contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: O padrão é <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see langword="Name" /> attribute of the Target element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: O atributo <see langword="Name" /> do elemento Target na coleção.

trans-unit.source: Gets the specified <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> object in the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o objeto <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> especificado no <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> object that contains the <see cref="P:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target.Name" /> property value specified by <paramref name="index" />.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target" /> objeto que contém o <see cref="P:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target.Name" /> especificado pelo valor da propriedade <paramref name="index" />.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> object represents a `Target` element in the project.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Target> objeto representa um `Target` elemento no projeto.

trans-unit.source: The <see langword="Name" /> attribute of the <see langword="Target" /> element to remove.
trans-unit.target: O atributo <see langword="Name" /> do elemento <see langword="Target" /> a ser removido.

trans-unit.source: Removes the specified [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) element from the project.
trans-unit.target: Remove o elemento [Target](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/350f6fc2-86b3-45f2-a31e-ece0e6bd4dca) especificado do projeto.

trans-unit.source: Gets an object that can be used to synchronize access to the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um objeto que pode ser usado para sincronizar o acesso ao <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: An object that can be used to synchronize access to the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto que pode ser usado para sincronizar o acesso ao <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.TargetCollection" />.
